title: $1450 / 1br - Private 1-Bedroom with Utilities
posting_body: ['A lower level in-law/one bedroom in Daly City located near San Francisco State University, three malls (Serramonte, Stonestown, & Westlake), two BART stations (Daly City and Colma), two Sam Trans bus lines (120, 121), two laundromats, and plenty of restaurants.', 'This unit does not have a kitchen and does not have access to a washer and dryer.', 'This is an ideal place for someone who values privacy and eats out quite often.', 'The in-law has:', '- A private entrance', '- A private bathroom', '- A spacious living room', '- New wall', 'to wall carpeting', '- A mini refrigerator and microwave', '- Available street parking', '- A spacious backyard, if you like to garden', 'The rent includes basic wifi, electricity, water, and garbage for a single household.', 'The monthly rent is $1450.', 'Move-in would require an $1,000+ deposit and first month’s rent totaling $2,450.', 'We would prefer one occupant, but open to having a maximum of two occupants for an increased rent amount (to be determined later).', 'Sorry no pets, no smoking, no drugs of any kind, and no illegal activities.', 'Please tell us about yourself in an email.', 'We will consider offers on a first come, first served basis via e-mail.', 'A credit check will be processed.', 'Thank you for viewing.']
